CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Landsea Homes Corp is a homebuilding company. It designs and builds best-in-class homes and sustainable master-planned communities in some of the nation's most desirable markets. The company's segments include Arizona, California, Florida, Metro New York, and Texas. It derives a majority of revenue from California.
